    SUM(oi.quantity) AS total_items_sold,
    COALESCE(SUM(ar.quantity_returned), 0) AS total_items_returned,
    CASE 
        WHEN SUM(oi.quantity) = 0 THEN 0
        ELSE COALESCE(SUM(ar.quantity_returned), 0)::DECIMAL / SUM(oi.quantity)
    END AS return_rate

JOIN orders o ON oi.order_id = o.order_id
JOIN products p ON oi.product_id = p.product_id
LEFT JOIN categories c ON p.category_id = c.category_id
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT ar.item_id, oi2.quantity AS quantity_returned
    FROM approved_returns ar
    JOIN order_items oi2 ON ar.item_id = oi2.item_id
) ar ON oi.item_id = ar.item_id
GROUP BY c.name
ORDER BY return_rate DESC;
